         I do the same as Ronaan.  With the 15 minute refresh time on QVoX and harmshield I keep them loaded all the time.  I usually keep fd up also.  When I'm travelling I keep gate/root up on top of those.</P><P>The reasoning is: they save your life a lot, they have a long refresh time, dots and other spells can be interchanged quickly for no loss of safety (i.e. cast funeral pyre, pryocuror, sit-med, mem splurt, plague, cast those two, sit-med, mem funeral pyre, cessation, etc etc.).  I usually keep up a lifetap also.</P><P>&lt;center&gt;<BR>&lt;a href=<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=177765&gt;Drainer" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=177765&gt;Drainer</a> the Heretic &lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;<BR>Warlock on Luclin &lt;br&gt;<BR>Legacy of Sorrow &lt;br&gt;<BR>Leader of Group 9 &lt;br&gt;<BR>&lt;/center&gt;<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
